Act, 7 U.S.C. §§ 7801–7813.

6 Dr. Ronald W. Ward, ‘‘Beef Demand and the Rate-of-Return to the U.S. Beef Checkoff,’’ Sep-
tember  2004,  http://www.beefboard.org/uDocs/wardstudy-2004.pdf;  Agricultural  Marketing
