cation  Programs  for  the  Photovoltaic  Industry—Status  and  Plans.  February
2003.
• Barbara  Martin  (FSEC),  Jane  M.  Weissman  (IREC),  Mark  Fitzgerald  (ISP).
A National Program for Certifying Solar Electric Practitioners. Proceedings at
the  8th  International  Symposium  on  Renewable  Energy  Education.  August
2002.
