62

trades  who  know  their  trade  very  well  may  not  know  solar  very
well, and so certainly training is very important on the actual, you
know,  the  characteristics  of  solar  and  the  technology  and  what  is
needed  to  put  up  a  good  system.  So  what  we  are  finding  and  you
know,  what  we  are  seeing  now  too  with  more  incentives  going  on
both  at  the  State  level  and  the  federal  level,  is  what  we  want  to
prevent  is  any  guy  or  gal  with  a  truck  and  a  ladder  to  think  they
can  put  this  stuff  up  on  the  roof.  That  is  not  true.  You  know,  it
is  going  to  be  a  problem.  So  that  even  those  people  that  may  feel
