20 years, grandfather me in, and we said absolutely not; we are not
going  to  give  you  a  seal  of  approval.  You  know,  if  you  know  what
you  are  doing,  you  are  going  to  pass  this  four-hour  exam  and,  you
know,  that  will  show  proof  that  we  can  give  you  the  certification
mark. So we are pretty serious in terms of making sure that if we
are  going  to  certify  somebody,  they  know  what  they  are  doing  and
prevent  some  of  the  stories  that  we  have  heard  or  that  we  have
seen,  some  of  the  mistakes  that  have  been  made,  some  of  the  stu-
pid  mistakes  that  have  been  made  out  in  the  field.  What  we  want
to  make  sure  is  customers  are  going  to  get,  you  know,  a  well-run
system that is going to last a long time.

Mr.  RESCH.  And  just  to  add  one  other  comment.  The  IBEW  has
