63

cause  of  the  benefits  that  you  accrue,  and  I  was  told  that  taking
down  the  tree  but  at  the  same  time  installing  the  system  was  the
equivalent of planting 100 more trees. So I hope that sales job was
accurate. This was a learning process for myself and my family.

I  thank  the  Chairwoman  for  her  indulgence  and  for  holding  this
very, very important hearing. These technologies and what our eco-
