A6. Again,  I  believe  I  don’t  have  the  expertise  to  adequately  answer  this  question.
Q7. What  enforcement  by  the  Secretary  of  Energy  do  you  envision  that  might  war-
rant civil penalty for noncompliance under section 10 of this bill? Is this section
